{"tid":1923904,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"【繪圖】肺炎是屬於中國的，得閒去做民間記者會最新問卷調查。","createTime":"2020-03-13T10:40:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T12:27:49.000Z","uid":164047,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3078c09a235e42808c68f0f8402b403925fc9952","tid":1923904,"uid":164047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T10:40:05.000Z","msg":"想畫下圖，幫下手。<br />\n但唔知仲可以畫咩。<br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h0OEOsD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh0OEOsD.jpg&h=03e33aee&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n突發！唔可以畀支那洗白！香港網軍主線任務！我要全世界都見到呢幅圖！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fgBsLS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fgBsLS</a><br />\n <br />\n2.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dJdpZzh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdJdpZzh.jpg&h=5adea227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民間記者會最新問卷調查<br />\n《立法會選舉前期民意調查》<br />\n<br />\n進唔進攻功能組別？有冇初選？點睇獨立？有關議題開始湧現民間，民間記者會想透過問卷調查了解民間聲音，希望同路人之間可以帶出更清晰取向同意見。<br />\n大家一齊入嚟填問卷，表達你嘅諗法啦！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.citizenspc.org/survey\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.citizenspc.org%2Fsurvey&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCVKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=ab292a72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.citizenspc.org/survey</a><br />\n<br />\n截止時間：3月15日晚上六時<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20d4adc0333fc093328acbec2117c332fe4e25ac","tid":1923904,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T10:46:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"66e2a372b16a8e558a53ac58c4ceb8423ac9dd19","tid":1923904,"uid":308262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T10:55:01.000Z","msg":"g 持！"},{"pid":"3e204fc7ba06e597ac93ed7aede5e19ab0e93921","tid":1923904,"uid":164047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:27:49.000Z","msg":"Thx.<img sr